item.title: 1.4.0 beta
item.description:
• Auto-determined BPMs are now being saved
  • A beats player has been introduced. Just type/paste the beats (like &a1 &2 for a Basic) and set a speed (beats per minute) and hear how it sounds

item.title: 1.4.1 beta
item.description:
• Fix Song remembers it has no positions, so new positions won't be loaded until the song is refreshed
  • Small UI changes with big effects to the player

item.title: 1.4.3 beta
item.description:
• Support symlinks in music and PDF directories (see this link for further details about symlinks)
  • Fixed a bug that caused mp3s to be created if, for some reason, they don't exist upon loading them into the player

item.title: 1.4.4 beta
item.description: • Fixed issue with macOS 11 Big Sur

item.title: 1.4.5 beta
item.description: • Fixed crash in playlists, if no song has been selected and the remove button is clicked

item.title: 1.4.6 beta
item.description: • Fixed an issue where history items would not be displayed with the correct time, if daylight savings time was in effect

item.title: 1.4.7 beta
item.description: • Added Ability to make the position table automatically scroll the currently active position in the song into the center of view

item.title: 1.4.8 beta
item.description:
• Native M1 / Pro / Max. support
  • Supportability: Song Log added in ~/Library/Application Support/ClogAmpSwift

item.title: 1.4.9 beta
item.description:
• Fixed a crash when importing positions
  • Minor UI overhaul

item.title: 1.5.0 beta
item.description:
• Fix crash when loading a song
  • Fix crash in playlists when a row without song is selected
  • Fix crash when importing positions with time < 0
  • Fix crash when reading the file path of a song
  • Add invisible buttons to increase and decrease the current songs playback speed (and volume)

item.title: 1.5.1 beta
item.description:
1.5.1

  • Adjustments of all tables
    • The last column is now fixed to the end of the table
    • If the last column has been previously adjusted, it'll might not be at the end of the table.
      => In this case reduce the window width so the column reaches the end of the table.
  • Wrapping positions!

item.title: 1.5.2 beta
item.description:
1.5.2

  • Fix alignments of textfields in the position tab

item.title: 1.5.4 beta
item.description:
1.5.4

  • Scroll to top on play
  • Fix crash when copying PDF data to positions
  • Resize position rows after changing description text

item.title: 1.5.5 beta
item.description:
1.5.5

  • Fix an issue with positions not being saved properly

item.title: 1.5.7 beta
item.description:
1.5.7

  • Fix issues during song loading due to PDF assignments
  • Improve performance loading

1.5.8
